&quot;I&#039;ll admit some knights do not adhere as strictly to their codes as I might, but I never said I lusted after the King&#039;s daughter!&quot;
 
&quot;You did! You were hoping you&#039;d be offered her hand upon report of my being slain!&quot;
 
